"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10025586\">",
"      Warning",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10025588\">",
"      What is this drug used for?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10025587\">",
"      What do I need to tell my doctor before I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10025592\">",
"      What are some things I need to know or do while I take this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10025593\">",
"      What are some side effects of this drug?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10025595\">",
"      What are some side effects that I need to call my doctor about right away?",
"     </a>",
"    </li>",
"    <li class=\"plainItem\">",
"     <a class=\"outlineLink\" href=\"#F10025590\">",
"      How is this drug best taken?",
"     </a>",
